casebody.data:
WOMACK NEWSPAPERS
v.
KITTY HAWK. No. 82PA07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 8, 2007. Hugh Stevens, Michael J. Tadych, Raleigh, for Womack Newspapers.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 8th day of February 2007 by Defendants (Harris, et al.) to Withdraw Petition:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 8th day of March 2007."
